msgctxt "0001"
msgid "Makoto! You ready for me to tell your fortune!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0002"
msgid "I told you, I'm done with that!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0003"
msgid ""
"C'mon, don't be like that! This one's <CLT 3>on me<CLT>! <CLT 3>Free\n"
"of charge<CLT>! <CLT 3>No money down<CLT>!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0004"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>That just makes me even more suspicious...\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0005"
msgid ""
"I'll be waiting for you in my room! Meet me as soon as\n"
"you can!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0006"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>I'm super skeptical...but I can't just ignore him.\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0007"
msgid "I guess I'd better just go and get this over with..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0008"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>But I'll have to be on my guard. This could be another\n"
"one of his traps...\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0009"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>Considering how he's been up till now, there's no way\n"
"I can believe he'd do anything for free.\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0010"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>Against my better judgment, I headed to Hiro's room...\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0011"
msgid "Yo, Makoto! Welcome!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0012"
msgid "Th-Thanks..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0013"
msgid ""
"Listen, before we get to the reading, I have a little\n"
"favor to ask..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0014"
msgid "I knew it!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0015"
msgid ""
"Forget it, I'm out of here! I was right to be\n"
"skeptical—!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0016"
msgid ""
"No, man! I'm for super serious this time!\n"
"Er—I mean, I really am serious!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0017"
msgid "I want to talk to you about a problem I'm having..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0018"
msgid "A problem?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0019"
msgid ""
"I listen to everyone else's problems all day, right?\n"
"But who do *I* have to talk to?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0020"
msgid "Friends? Nope. I mean I literally have zero friends..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0021"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>Jeez... I figured he didn't have many friends, but\n"
"none at all...?\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0022"
msgid ""
"This is the first time I've felt like there was\n"
"someone I could talk to, could share my problems with."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0023"
msgid "H-Hiro..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0024"
msgid ""
"Okay. If you don't mind telling me, I don't mind\n"
"listening."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0025"
msgid "Thanks...!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0026"
msgid ""
"So, you remember I told you how I got held back a few\n"
"times, right?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0027"
msgid "Y-Yeah, you mentioned that."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0028"
msgid "Well, there's kind of a <CLT 3>serious reason<CLT> for that."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0029"
msgid "There is...?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0030"
msgid "Someone's <CLT 3>after me<CLT>."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0031"
msgid "Someone's after you? Who!? What did you do!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0032"
msgid ""
"No, I—what makes you think I did anything? I just got\n"
"dragged into it."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0033"
msgid ""
"I had an appointment come in, the daughter of some\n"
"rich upper management type guy."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0034"
msgid ""
"Maaaybe I pressured her a little to pull out her\n"
"entire life savings..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0035"
msgid ""
"Well, when her dad found out, he went apepoop, and it\n"
"turned into a whole legal thing..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0036"
msgid "..."
msgstr "..."

msgctxt "0037"
msgid ""
"And it turns out, this Mr. Richie Rich guy just so\n"
"happened to have ties to the mob."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0038"
msgid ""
"So then I had these super scary gangsters coming after\n"
"me...!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0039"
msgid "And you tried to run?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0040"
msgid "Yeah. But they caught up to me, of course."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0041"
msgid ""
"They tried to force me to pay them...well, more than I\n"
"could afford. So I snuck my way into Hope's Peak..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0042"
msgid ""
"The instant I leave this school, they're gonna come\n"
"for my guts! Black market organs are in huge demand!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0043"
msgid ""
"But I love my organs! I don't wanna give 'em to\n"
"someone else!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0044"
msgid ""
"So, here's the deal. Sell me some of your organs on\n"
"the cheap, and I can resell 'em at market price!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0045"
msgid "..."
msgstr "..."

msgctxt "0046"
msgid "Just one! One's all I need!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0047"
msgid "..."
msgstr "..."

msgctxt "0048"
msgid ""
"Okay, fine! Sell me your identity! Those are pretty\n"
"valuable these days!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0049"
msgid "..."
msgstr "..."

msgctxt "0050"
msgid "Gah...! You're so selfish!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0051"
msgid ""
"Be honest, you used that money to buy those artifacts\n"
"of yours, didn't you?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0052"
msgid "Gwah! H-How'd you know!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0053"
msgid ""
"I remember you mentioning how expensive that stuff\n"
"was. What else could it be?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0054"
msgid ""
"Wait! Y-You're not suggesting I sell my OOPArts, are\n"
"you!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0055"
msgid ""
"Why not? That makes the most sense, doesn't it? If you\n"
"can't bear to do it yourself, I'll help you."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0056"
msgid ""
"No! No no no! No freakin' way! That collection is all\n"
"I have in life!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0057"
msgid ""
"How could you even suggest such a terrible thing!\n"
"You're a cruel man, Makoto Naegi!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0058"
msgid "You can call it terrible, but—"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0059"
msgid "That's enough! Forget I ever asked!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0060"
msgid ""
"No matter what it takes, I'm gonna get out of here!\n"
"Even if it means demolishing my life savings!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0061"
msgid "Wait, you have life savings!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0062"
msgid "Tch. So now you know."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0063"
msgid ""
"I figured if I sold your organs, I wouldn't have to\n"
"dip into my retirement fund..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0064"
msgid "What the hell is wrong with you!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0065"
msgid ""
"What!? Okay, I've had it! If you're not gonna give me\n"
"your organs OR your identity, you can just get out!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0066"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>Hiro angrily sent me away, and I was glad to go.\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0067"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>In the end, I think I'm better off having talked to\n"
"him about...all of this.\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0068"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>If nothing else, I got to know him a lot better.\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0069"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>I learned to never let my guard down around him...\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0070"
msgid ""
"Could what we have be described as a kind\n"
"of...<CLT 3>friendship<CLT>?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0071"
msgid ""
"<CLT 23>Hiro's <CLT><CLT 3>Report Card<CLT><CLT 23> has been updated based on your\n"
"experience with him.\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0072"
msgid ""
"<CLT 23>Your maximum number of <CLT><CLT 3>Skill Points<CLT><CLT 23> has increased!\n"
"Hey, look at you go!\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0073"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>I couldn't stop thinking about what he'd said, so I\n"
"just went back to my room.\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""
